                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her sweet Weight on my Heart a Night</l>
                    <l>Had scarcely deigned to lie --</l>
                    <l>When, stirring, for Belief's delight,</l>
                    <l>My Bride had slipped away --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>If 'twas a Dream -- made solid -- just</l>
                    <l>The Heaven to confirm --</l>
                    <l>Or if Myself were dreamed of Her --</l>
                    <l>The <app type="revision"><lem>wisdom</lem><rdg>wisdom</rdg></app>
power to presume --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Him remain -- who unto Me --</l>
                    <l>Gave -- even as to All --</l>
                    <l>A Fiction superseding Faith --</l>
                    <l>By so much -- as 'twas real --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                </lg>

